      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service records. Clean title. No accidents. Garage kept.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and the 'new car' scent lingers. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships. It has never seen snow or salt, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer or collector to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 48500.0,
